            <lg xml:id="TK657">
<l>paḻimalain teytiya vākkattiṟ cāṉṟōr </l>
<l>kaḻinal kuravē talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Far more excellent is the extreme poverty of the wise than wealth obtained by heaping up of sinful deeds.</l>
